data.description: Welcome to this charming property located in the popular coastal community of Pointe Alexis. Seller has a This well maintained home boasts neutral and tasteful updates including new luxury vinyl flooring throughout the main living areas. The kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances and an eat-in dinette area. Enjoy the spacious open floor plan with living room/dining room combo and a cozy wood burning fireplace. The mater bedroom is large and includes an office/sitting area, a walk-in closet, plus 3 additional closets and master bath ensuite with dual sinks and granite countertops. Lovely french doors lead out to a private rear screened in patio! This community is maintenance free and has many amenities including an olympic size pool, tennis courts, fitness center, billiard room and clubhouse - Florida Resort Style living at its best! Conveniently located close to the beach, Fred Howard Park and the historic sponge docks with great restaurants and shopping. (Roof 2018/Air Conditioner 2015)  NOTE- SELLER HAS A TRANSFERRABLE 3% MORTGAGE AND TRANSFERABLE FLOOD INSURANCE!
